      • JSONParser

        public JSONParser(String json)
        Returns a JSONParser for some string input JSON. This constructor should be used when constructing a programmatic pipeline, such as piping the JSON output of a program into the SurveyMan language and runtime system. If the data is instead staged, use makeParser.
        Parameters:
        json - The JSON representation of a survey.
